
Account has many Spaces
Account has many line items
Account has one profile

Member belongs to account
Member has many spaces
Member belongs to Spaces
Member has many line items
Member has one profile
Member has many roles
Member belongs to Team

Space has many plan types
Space has many members
Space has many modules

Plan has many resources (10 visits)

Pass has many resources (days, desks, lockers)

Resource 

Line Item has one polymorphic (plan, resource, pass)

Team has many members


